# Project Structure (Setup Tutorial Website)

- Next.js App Router (v15) with server components. Main layout: [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx). Global styles: [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css).
- Home page: [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx). Documentation sections live under `src/app/*/page.tsx` (e.g., [src/app/quickstart/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/quickstart/page.tsx), [src/app/how-to-use/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/how-to-use/page.tsx), [src/app/project-overview/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/project-overview/page.tsx)).
- Tool docs dynamic route: [src/app/tools/[slug]/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/tools/[slug]/page.tsx)
  - Uses static generation via `generateStaticParams`
  - Requires awaiting `params` before accessing properties (Next 15 async params)
  - Loads markdown content from [content/each-tool-explained/](mdc:content/each-tool-explained)
- Shared UI components: [src/components/](mdc:src/components)
- Config: [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts), [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json), [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs), [postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs)
- Public assets: [public/](mdc:public)

